New-ADGroup -Name CompassAppConnectUser -GroupCategory Security -GroupScope Global -Path $OU -Description "Staff with this permission are able to use the Connect feature and chat with other staff. They can also chat with students they teach or have taught and parents associated with those students if Parent and Student Connect access is enabled."
New-ADGroup -Name CompassAppConnectPower -GroupCategory Security -GroupScope Global -Path $OU -Description "Staff with this permission are to use the Connect feature to chat with other staff. They can also chat with any student or parent across the school if Parent and Student Connect access is enabled."
New-ADGroup -Name CompassAppConnectAdmin -GroupCategory Security -GroupScope Global -Path $OU -Description "Staff with this permission are to use the Connect feature to chat with other staff. They can also chat with any student or parent across the school if Parent and Student Connect access is enabled.This permission also allows staff to manage which staff have the ConnectPower permission."
New-ADGroup -Name CompassAppContinuumAdmin -GroupCategory Security -GroupScope Global -Path $OU -Description "Ability to update and edit any Continuum result throughout Compass. Also allows the user to manage which progressions are available to staff in Compass."
New-ADGroup -Name CompassAppContinuumPower -GroupCategory Security -GroupScope Global -Path $OU -Description "Ability to update (edit) the continuum results from the activity/class page for an activity that they manage (are the lead teacher). Also includes all permissions associated with ContinuumView."
New-ADGroup -Name CompassAppContinuumView -GroupCategory Security -GroupScope Global -Path $OU -Description "Has read-only access to all Continuum results, including the continuum tab on activities they can see and any student's profile."
